---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ScrollIndicator from '../../components/ScrollIndicator.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Free Solar & Energy Consultation Geelong | Book Online | EES"
  description="Free no-obligation energy consultation in Geelong. We assess your property and recommend the best solar, battery or heat pump solution."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Free Energy Consultation</h1>
      <p>No-obligation assessment of your property and energy needs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>What Happens During a Consultation</h2>
      <p>
        We visit your property and carry out a detailed assessment. This isn't a sales pitch — it's an engineering assessment to determine what system will actually work best for your situation.
      </p>
      <p>During the visit, we'll:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Assess your roof</strong> — orientation, pitch, shading, and available space for solar panels</li>
        <li><strong>Review your energy bills</strong> — understand how much you use, when you use it, and what you're paying</li>
        <li><strong>Discuss your goals</strong> — whether that's reducing bills, going off-grid, replacing gas, adding a battery, or all of the above</li>
        <li><strong>Evaluate your electrical setup</strong> — switchboard capacity, existing wiring, and what's needed for installation</li>
        <li><strong>Recommend a system</strong> — based on your property, not a generic package</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What You'll Receive</h2>
      <p>
        After your consultation, we provide a detailed proposal that includes:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>System design and component specifications</li>
        <li>Expected energy generation and savings</li>
        <li>Applicable rebates (STC, Victorian Government rebates)</li>
        <li>Itemised pricing — no hidden costs</li>
        <li>Financing options if needed</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        There's no obligation and no pressure. If you decide to proceed, we handle everything from paperwork to installation. If not, you keep the assessment.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Credentials</h2>
      <p>
        EES is a CEC-accredited installer and Solar Victoria approved retailer. Every consultation is conducted by a qualified member of our team — not a subcontractor or third-party sales agent.
      </p>

      <h2>Service Area</h2>
      <p>
        We service Greater Geelong, Torquay, the Surf Coast, Bellarine Peninsula, Golden Plains, and wider regional Victoria. Based in Moolap, we're a local team with local knowledge.
      </p>

      <h2>Book Your Consultation</h2>
      <p>
        Ready to find out what's possible for your property? Get in touch and we'll arrange a time that works for you.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:0427664827">0427 664 827</a></li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@eeservices.io">support@eeservices.io</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Or use the <a href="#solar-qualifier">energy assessment tool</a> at the bottom of this page to get started online.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <ScrollIndicator />
</BaseLayout>
